content: I have a resource profile (structuredefinition-Contract-eltss.xml) and the build server isn't using the version in Github. How do I force it to use the version there and not an old version?
The differential view (http://build.fhir.org/ig/HL7/eLTSS/Contract-eltss.html) doesn't match the actual differential in the xml
It's not a sparse differential problem as the elements show up but their description isn't being updated.
No, wait, I found it. Sorry to bother you.
